 {"id":"asupersync-8w83i.3.2","title":"[FABRIC][P2.2] Cx integration for subject capabilities","description":"Integrate subject capability grants into the Cx capability context. File: src/messaging/capability/mod.rs

- Each subject prefix or transform space granted through explicit capabilities in Cx
- Capability grant lowers to: owned token type for in-process Rust paths AND runtime capability check for distributed paths
